You can use the following pattern:

1. Map your list/array to async jobs
2. Map list of async jobs to their result

In code, it&#39;d look like this

    myData.map { data -&gt;
        async {
            callToServer(data)
        }
    }.map {
        it.await()
    }

This would run each callToServer in separate job concurrently.

